Class OfficerRegistrationRepository

java.lang.Object
main.repository.FileBasedRepository<OfficerRegistration,String>
main.repository.OfficerRegistrationRepository
All Implemented Interfaces:
Repository<OfficerRegistration,String>
public class OfficerRegistrationRepository extends FileBasedRepository<OfficerRegistration,String>
Repository class for managing officer registrations to projects. Uses project name as the unique project identifier.
